@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #85099 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
I suppose unsound on stable would be P-high again? This is no regression; I tagged a bunch of teams in the issue mostly following the labeling of #66544.
Unsound on stable is P-critical if the unsoundness can be triggered by accident.
I don't think this can happen on accident, would say P-high
I also think a P-high is ok here. Since the discussion about this unsoundness started last year I wonder if T-lang should have a look at that again (issue is already labeled T-lang)
As far as I understand, T-lang looks at all P-high+T-lang issues anyways in triage meetings.
Alright, Iâ€™m just the creator of the issue; apparently only team members can assign the priorities, so anyone that can do it, feel free ^^
Oh, wait, this has already been prio-d.
